"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRbjkWN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRbjkWN.png&h=6cd179da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0658b3ba85687df8a7886a2bfbf9a481757a55d6","tid":1421291,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:16:24.000Z","msg":"經過上次教訓一個刀手都無出現過，仲相信呢d新聞傳言吹風，係唔係傻㗎"},{"pid":"c56fbbf71af4b8ee02f4ef6dfbf3d0cfb62c4be0","tid":1421291,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52e9ff08dc12efe7e42fca99f492f70369e6cdd5","tid":1421291,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRbjkWN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRbjkWN.png&h=6cd179da&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:35:28.000Z","msg":"你好明顯係鬼, 一向宗旨都係保護自己保護同路人齊進齊退, 你叫人追擊即係挑釁引戰想件究事鬧大做新聞"},{"pid":"631a36d8a3f7d47c36c45951f7659c4df717b4e9","tid":1421291,"uid":293113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"c3fe43f6811d0af23c31af4083fdea51952a5b84","tid":1421291,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:05:35.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"d4b46d8ebdbe4bc3339b4f86e2eb2926c7d799c0","tid":1421291,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e90cebeba8b1a7f7381d683db3b101163070306f","tid":1421291,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: large;\">微訊群<br />\n<br />\n福建呀叔落到街俾黑衣人用福建話屌返轉頭<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FaTvrfUcjZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFaTvrfUcjZM&d=rGhbZie%2F6bi%2FABGI9SBXCuDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=10991a9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FaTvrfUcjZM</a><br />\n\t</blockquote>哇屌竟然係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開頭講野個阿叔應該識打人個幾個福建幫，佢話：&rdquo;打輸左喇 打輸左喇！屌佢老味⋯遊行入面混左個班係自己福建人嚟嘅⋯⋯班仆街混左入遊行人士度帶人返自己北角搞搞陣，捉到一個喺度打先講福建話話係自己人&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n佢意思係想話放風叫佢去等黑衫打黑衫係比人跌9左，原來係有幾個福建鬼混左入遊行人士入面引其他黑衫人去北角同佢哋打！<br />\n<br />\n好撚鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>(借朋友account post)<br />\n<br />\n呢位巴打應該有少少理解錯左。<br />\n<br />\n頭2段錄音個阿叔係話，同黑衫後生仔開拖打果陣，就聽到有後生仔話自己其實都係福建人。<br />\n<br />\n所以佢個錄音係屌啲黑衫：「明明係同鄕啲仔女，都仲帶人番北角（自己屋企地頭）搞搞震，所以班後生係抵打、應該要打得佢地再甘啲、教訓下佢地」。<br />\n<br />\n而唔係話有福建鬼混入遊行人士然後特登引大家落北角俾人打咁解。<br />\n<br />\n想澄清番，希望大家唔好誤會同路人。<br />\n<br />\n不分化，不割蓆。<br />\n不要讓仇恨蒙蔽，堅持五大訴求。</blockquote>我冇可能解錯, 我搵左幾個母語既黎聽同都咁講<br />\n福建自己人流傳都係話比人擺上抬<br />\n仲有福建人D仔女日日參加遊行唔係新聞, <br />\n仲有尋日有鬼冇啦啦吹風帶頭去北角都有幾個post印證左<br />\n呢班帶風向既就係鬼"}]}